relation: A tribute to the completion of Zargata's "Fishing for Kraken" comic series (http://starmen.net/comics/series/fishkraken/), in the form of a coloured Krakenist.

Jeff, with the big guns. The bazooka's likely more than a bit too tapered to be in anywhere near good perspective, but I enjoyed this one anyway. Thanks to mistycat85 for having pointed out a flaw in a previous version. :)
A depiction of the Starman Jr. from the second chapter of the Ubsey Movies "EarthBound Saga".
A depiction of Robbie Benson as Ness if he continues to let his facial hair grow, from "EarthBound Saga" by Ubsey Movies.
